description:
The image is Purely Original without any editing.

It’s Swiss Military 6 in 1 Bluetooth Speaker (BL-3).
I brought this new amazingly beautiful speaker, When i turned it on in night, it reminded me of a wallpaper which i downloaded from unsplash few months back.

Then i tried to remake the scene.

Inspired by the wallpaper i downloaded from unsplash (https://unsplash.com/photos/ZPP-zP8HYG0)
We wanted to display the concept of a person thinking. We entered a dark room, spent a long time adjusting the light, and came up with this image.
